result.longName: Millennium Group Corporation (Asia) Public Company Limited

assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Millennium Group Corporation (Asia) Public Company Limited engages in the wholesale and retail of automobiles, yachts, and spare parts primarily in Thailand. The company is involved in the buying, selling, renting, and provision of services for automotives. It also offers after-sales services, including selling automotive parts, decorative accessories, clothing, and other products; body paint and repair services; and car rental services under the Sixt Rent brand name. In addition, the company provides car maintenance and other services, chauffeur services, computer system installation, telephone system, computer program, human resource development, marketing management services, insurance brokerage, and leasing for vehicles and escorting customers for private jet services. Further, it offers information technology (IT) solutions, including other IT consulting services, customer interaction center, data analysis, digital marketing, and training center for automotive industries; insurance and risk management solutions; and management services. Millennium Group Corporation (Asia) Public Company Limited was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand. Millennium Group Corporation (Asia) Public Company Limited  operates as a subsidiary of Tham Holdings Co., Ltd.
